        "core/5.7.3.6.txt",
        "opal/4.3.5.4.txt",
        rule="Set changes selected table cells and returns an empty result list on success. Object.Set must omit Where. Table.Set on an object table must include Where as a UID and its Values must be RowValues. Table.Set on a byte table may omit Where or use Row addressing, and its Values must be Bytes. Omitting Values from an otherwise correct Set invocation succeeds with no effect.",
