        "core/5.1.3.82.txt",
        rule="CreateLog requires NewLogTableName, HighSecurity, and MinSize. HighSecurity has boolean type, whose valid values are integer 0/False and 1/True. MinSize and optional HintSize have uinteger type. A successful invocation returns exactly LogListUID, LogTableUID, and Rows.",
