        rule="DeleteMethod, GetACL, AddACE, and RemoveACE are meta-methods invoked on AccessControlTableUID. DeleteMethod and GetACL require InvokingID and MethodID. AddACE and RemoveACE require InvokingID, MethodID, and ACE. GetACL returns Result as an access_control_list, specifically a list of ACE uidrefs. AddACE, RemoveACE, and DeleteMethod return an empty result list on success; success or failure is otherwise determined by the status code.",
