        rule="The Locking SP AccessControl preconfiguration includes the concrete ThisSP/RevertSP association, and Opal gives the RevertSP signature as ThisSP.RevertSP. That row's GetACLACL is ACE_Admin, so unauthenticated GetACL for ThisSP/RevertSP is not authorized, while an Admin authority can retrieve the ACL. The same row has empty AddACEACL, RemoveACEACL, and DeleteMethodACL columns; those meta-methods are not invocable for the association. Because AccessControl meta-methods identify associations by exact InvokingID/MethodID, a LockingSP/RevertSP argument is not the same association as ThisSP/RevertSP.",
