        "opal/4.3.1.6.txt",
        "opal/4.3.1.7.txt",
        rule="GetACL retrieves the ACL column for an AccessControl association and returns the access_control_list as ACE uidrefs. Opal Locking SP preconfigures concrete AccessControl rows for Locking_GlobalRange Get/Set, K_AES_128 GlobalRange/Range1 Get/GenKey, and K_AES_256 GlobalRange/Range1 Get/GenKey. Therefore successful GetACL responses for those associations must return exactly the ACE uidrefs listed in the row's ACL column; returning a Range1 ACL for GlobalRange, a K_AES_256 ACE for K_AES_128, a GenKey ACE for Get, or an omitted Locking Set ACE is not compliant.",
