        "opal/4.2.1.6.txt",
        rule="GetACL returns the ACL column of the AccessControl association as a list of ACE uidrefs. Template_object_ref identifies object references within the Admin SP Template table. In the Admin SP AccessControl preconfiguration, the Template object wildcard Get row has ACL ACE_Anybody and GetACLACL ACE_Anybody. Therefore successful GetACL for TemplateTable/Get, whether addressed by symbolic table name or by the Template object table UID, must return ACE_Anybody exactly; returning ACE_Admin or an empty ACL is not protocol-compliant.",
