        "core/5.3.3.14.5.txt",
        "core/5.3.4.3.1.txt",
        "core/5.3.4.3.2.txt",
        "core/5.3.4.3.3.txt",
        "opal/4.2.1.5.txt",
        "opal/4.2.1.6.txt",
        rule="The Admin SP AccessControl row for SPInfo/Get has ACL ACE_Anybody and AddACEACL ACE_Anybody, while RemoveACEACL, GetACLACL, and DeleteMethodACL are empty. Therefore AddACE can append a valid ACE to that ACL and returns an empty result, but GetACL, RemoveACE, and DeleteMethod remain not authorized for that association. Failed meta-method attempts do not mutate the ACL or tombstone the association. The AddACE duplicate rule is evaluated against the current ACL, including successful prior AddACE calls, and state persists across sessions.",
